 
                        ..  
                      / __)  All that is gold does not glitter, Not all those who wander are lost;
               .-^^^-/ /    The old that is strong does not wither, Deep roots are not reached by the frost.
            __/       /   From the ashes a fire shall be woken, A light from the shadows shall spring;
           <__.|_|-|_|   Renewed shall be blade that was broken, The crownless again shall be king.
                                                                                                                     